data.description: This property has everything you could want, and more! Tucked within the Rolling Hills outside of the city limits you will find a spacious home, a heated & cooled 30x40 shop and a 20x20 storage building, all sitting on 1.36 acres, away from the hustle and bustle of city life but still close to 287 and the loop. The shop is a mechanic/hobbyist dream! The shop features spray foam insulation, a vehicle lift, air compressors, brand new mini-split for heating and air, a wood burning stove that will allow you to work and hang out in the shop even in the dead of winter, a point-to-point system for WiFi, security cameras, and much more! Additional updates include a new septic Inside the home, you will find a wonderful open layout with two living areas and a large kitchen. There are two primary bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms and a huge finished basement that is being used as the fourth bedroom. The large den has a bricked wall and gas starting wood burning fireplace that give the home a cozy feel all year long. Off the den is a wonderful covered patio. Please check out the entire list of updates, there is simply too many to list!
